narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: An undertstanding of political psychology as well as the study of affect as it relates to political theory. Professor Oskian is very attuned to thinking about method, and this is something that I will take beyond this course.
I had the opportunity to explore an array of diverse texts. I really enjoyed the class.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This course was fantastic. We read a really exciting range of texts, and classroom discussions were interesting. Professor Oskian is brilliant, and getting to hear her discuss these readings was a joy.
Absolutely! Professor Oskian is a wonderful instructor; she is incredibly supportive.
